@startuml component_architecture
!theme plain

title UIM Master Data Governance (MDG) - Component Architecture

actor "MDG Consumer\n(UI / Integration)" as Consumer

node "MDG Service Runtime" {
  component "MDGServer\n(vibe.d HTTP API)" as Server
  component "MDGService\n(Business Logic)" as Service
  database "MDGStore\n(In-Memory Tenant Data)" as Store
}

Consumer --> Server : REST API calls
Server --> Service : Route + validate request
Service --> Store : Read/Write business partners
Service --> Store : Read/Write quality rules

note right of Service
Core capabilities:
- governance workflow
- batch ingest
- duplicate detection + merge
- quality rule evaluation
end note

@enduml
